The paper focuses on –
* stating the vision and objectives of the plan;
* outlining the problems by way of a statement;
* describing the approaches to the implementation of the plan;
* articulating the management challenges;
* addressing the key performance areas, as outlined in the Disaster
* outlining the implementation guidelines.

